## Project

App: **Ngày Lành Tháng Tốt** (ngaytot / ngaylanhthangtot.vn)
Stack: React Router v7 (Vite) · Supabase (DB + Auth + RLS + Edge Functions) · Vercel · Tailwind CSS · Direction B design system (`app/components/brand/`)

## Architecture summary

- **Frontend:** React SPA on Vercel. Pre-render **`/`** for SEO. Authenticated app routes under **`/app/*`**.
- **Backend:** Supabase only. Client via publishable key + JWT; **RLS** is the auth boundary.
- **Server logic:** Edge Functions — **Bát Tự** proxy (`BAT_TU_*` secrets), **PayOS** checkout + webhook, share resolve/OG, `generate-reading` (Gemini), cron push. No PayOS, Bát Tự or Gemini calls from the browser.
- **Design:** Direction B — light-default paper surfaces for daily app; ceremonial forest-dark for readings, payment success, habit rituals. Source: `app/components/brand/` (Logo, LogoMark, Ticket, Stamp, Kanji, Mono, BackBar, BottomNav).

## What this app does

Vietnamese B2C PWA: pick auspicious dates (**chọn ngày**) and related insights using **Bát Tự Tứ Trụ**, **personalized by saved lá số**. **Credits + PayOS** (bundles/packs, no auto-renew). Anonymous users get **hôm nay** + **tuần này** free. Tone: calm, specific, Vietnamese.

## Not building (out of scope)

Generative chatbot; raw almanac tables as primary UI; marketplace thầy; community/UGC; AI-personalized push; non-Vi locale; admin dashboard; credit gifting; offline engine; auto-recurring subscriptions; **self-serve birth-data edit** (birth-data is set once at onboarding — no edit form anywhere in the app); **multi-person stored "family profiles"** (dropped in Direction B — not built at all).

## LLM / AI Reading (first-class feature)

AI Reading (Luận Giải) is first-class, powered by **Gemini Flash** via the `generate-reading` Edge Function. Engine = deterministic Bát Tự + Gemini templates. No generative chatbot. No raw LLM access from the browser. All calls go through the Edge proxy with credit gating.

## AI module boundary

Gemini calls live exclusively in `supabase/functions/generate-reading/`. No AI SDK in the React app. RLS + credit ledger enforce auth/payment boundary.

## Key constraints

- **Auth:** Google OAuth + email/password; **anonymous** browse for free calendar/teaser.
- **PayOS only** — no Stripe unless product changes.
- **Feature credit keys:** DB canonical names in `feature_credit_costs`.
- **PayOS `package_sku`:** `le`, `goi_6thang`, `goi_12thang` only. UI labels: "Lẻ — gói nhỏ" / "Tháng An Cư" / "Năm Phú Quý".
- **Screen inventory:** `app/routes/` + `artifacts/plans/build-plan.md`.

